OL,7,FKirsty-Leigh Porter has played Leela
OL,8,FLomax in Hollyoaks for more than ten
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FThis week sees her become Leela Dexter
OL,12,Fas she marries her on screen boyfriend
OL,13,FJoel Dexter, played by Rory Douglas-
OL,14,FSpeed - but there's heartache on the
OL,15,Fwedding night.
OL,17,FOur entertainment correspondent
OL,18,FCaroline Whitmore met up with Kirsty-
OL,19,F Leigh and Rory who play Leela and
OL,20,FJoel on the Hollyoaks set, in the
OL,21,FLomax family living room.
