OL,7,FThe actress had a stillborn baby girl,
OL,8,FPenny-Leigh, in 2018. Now her
OL,9,Fcharacter is going through the same
OL,10,Fpain.
OL,12,FShe said: "Yeah, if anyone was going
OL,13,Fto tell this story it was going to be
OL,14,Fme and it's a good way of trying to
OL,15,Fbreak the taboo and talk about baby
OL,16,Floss"
OL,18,F"I suffered a loss. Even five years
OL,19,Fago there wasn't much done to provide
OL,20,Fcare for parents that are suffering a
OL,21,Fbereavement"
