OL,7,F"I did my research" continues Rory "I
OL,8,Flooked at podcasts and different
OL,9,Fthings about these men who felt
OL,10,Fdefenseless and didn't know where to
OL,11,Fturn, didn't know who to speak to,
OL,12,Fdidn't feel like they had any input
OL,13,Fbecause it's not them that has
OL,14,Fexperienced the loss physically but
OL,15,Fmentally, they've lost everything. We
OL,16,Fthought it was so so powerful"
