OL,7,F"They've got six divisions of baby
OL,8,Floss awareness. They help you at
OL,9,Fdifferent stages of your loss. They
OL,10,Fwere a lifeline to me when I lost
OL,11,FPenny-Leigh, and they asked me to
OL,12,Fbecome an ambassador- I was so proud"
OL,14,F"And I just feel quite ready now to be
OL,15,Fable to do what I can to help the
OL,16,Ftrust and to help people" She smiles
OL,18,FNow, Kirsty-Leigh is mother to a
OL,19,Flittle girl.
