OL,7,F"She's three. She's a rainbow baby. If
OL,8,Fyou've suffered a loss, and you become
OL,9,Fpregnant again and you have a child,
OL,10,Fthey're known as rainbow babies purely
OL,11,Ffor the fact that after a storm comes
OL,12,Fa rainbow.J"And she's just brought a
OL,13,Flot of happiness and healing to me,
OL,14,Fwhich is I guess what they do"
OL,16,FIf you or someone close to you has
OL,17,Fexperienced baby loss there are plenty
OL,18,Fof ways to get support.
